          <placeName key="Luzern (Stadt)"><hi>Luzern</hi></placeName> d. <date when="1878-01-31">31. <choice><abbr><hi>Jan</hi>.</abbr><expan>Januar</expan></choice> 1878</date>.</p>
      </div>
